data.description:
Welcome to 340 S Festival, a sophisticated residence nestled in the heart of the vibrant Montecillo community in El Paso, TX. This smart urban home is a testament to modern living, offering a perfect blend of style, comfort, and innovation.

As you step into this inviting abode, you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-designed floor plan that seamlessly integrates luxury and functionality. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 3 baths, this residence is thoughtfully crafted to accommodate both relaxation and entertainment.

The highlight of this home is the presence of not one, but two master bedrooms, providing unparalleled flexibility for residents. Each master suite exudes a sense of tranquility and sophistication, featuring well-appointed en-suite bathrooms and ample closet space.
